    "Notably, those results are significantly higher than those reported in a glaucoma setting.",
    "We indeed hypothesize that surgical decisions in vitreoretinal surgery are much more limited and follow more precise hinges, when compared to the immensity of glaucoma surgical treatments and the possible overlap between them.",
